          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-1609943036546-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>creamy</strong> <strong>leek & mushroom pie filling</strong> to an <strong>oven-proof dish </strong>(or two!)</p><p>Dust your work surface with a generous sprinkling of <strong>flour</strong></p><p>Unwrap your <strong>puff pastry</strong> and roll it out to approx. 0.5cm thickness with a <strong>rolling pin</strong> and score a criss-cross pattern across the top with a knife</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
