    {
      "instruction": "<p>Lay the <strong>puff pastry</strong> sheet over the pie dish[es] and trim off any excess</p><p>Tip: Use any excess pastry to add decorations to the pie!</p><p>Press the edges with a fork to seal the pastry to the dish[es], then brush the <strong>reserved creamy</strong> <strong>single</strong> <strong>soy </strong>all over</p><p>Put the dish[es] in the oven for 20-25 min or until puffed up, golden and cooked through – this is your <strong>plant-based creamy leek & mushroom pie</strong></p>",
